<section class="py-24 px-4 border-t border-slate/50">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold font-mono text-cloud mb-4 text-balance reveal">
        Your shell history is a graveyard of lost context
      </h2>
      <p class="text-dust text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto text-pretty reveal">
        You ran the command. Your terminal forgot why.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 stagger-children">
      <!-- Pain 1 -->
      <div class="p-8 bg-slate/20 border border-slate rounded-2xl reveal">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 mb-6 rounded-xl bg-ember/10 flex items-center justify-center text-2xl">
          🔍
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold font-mono text-cloud mb-3">Re-Googling commands you know</h3>
        <p class="text-dust text-sm leading-relaxed">
          "How did I set up that Postgres container again?" You ran it two weeks ago.
          <code class="text-ember font-mono text-xs bg-ember/10 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded">history | grep docker</code>
          returns 400 lines of noise. No repo context. No directory. Good luck.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Pain 2 -->
      <div class="p-8 bg-slate/20 border border-slate rounded-2xl reveal">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 mb-6 rounded-xl bg-ember/10 flex items-center justify-center text-2xl">
          🔄
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold font-mono text-cloud mb-3">Rebuilding project context every time</h3>
        <p class="text-dust text-sm leading-relaxed">
          Clone a repo you worked on last month. What's the first command?
          <code class="text-ember font-mono text-xs bg-ember/10 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded">npm install</code>? 
          <code class="text-ember font-mono text-xs bg-ember/10 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded">docker compose up</code>?
          You waste 5 minutes remembering how to start the project.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Pain 3 -->
      <div class="p-8 bg-slate/20 border border-slate rounded-2xl reveal">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 mb-6 rounded-xl bg-ember/10 flex items-center justify-center text-2xl">
          🧠
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold font-mono text-cloud mb-3">Forgetting tools you installed</h3>
        <p class="text-dust text-sm leading-relaxed">
          You brew-installed 
          <code class="text-ember font-mono text-xs bg-ember/10 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded">fd</code>, 
          <code class="text-ember font-mono text-xs bg-ember/10 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded">ripgrep</code>, 
          <code class="text-ember font-mono text-xs bg-ember/10 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded">fzf</code>...
          then kept using 
          <code class="text-ember font-mono text-xs bg-ember/10 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded">find</code> 
          and 
          <code class="text-ember font-mono text-xs bg-ember/10 px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded">grep</code> 
          out of habit. Your terminal knows what you have. You don't.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
